          To deliver industrial intelligence that enables organizations to see everything, act faster, and command with confidence.
        </p>
      </div>
      <Placeholder label="Company Image" class="min-h-[300px]" />
    </div>
  </Section>

  <CtaBanner
    title="Join Our Journey"
    description="See how Quatro can transform your operations."
    primaryCta={{ label: 'Schedule a Demo', href: '/contact/demo' }}
    secondaryCta={{ label: 'View Careers', href: '/company/careers' }}
  />
</MarketingLayout>
